{"word":"G669 - ἀποφθέγγομαι - apophthéngomai - ap-of-theng'-om-ahee - Say","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀποφθέγγομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apophthéngomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-of-theng'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Say</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பேசு, என்று சொல்"},{"paragraph":"to speak out, speak forth, pronounce, to utter or declare oneself, give one's opinion"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G5350 - φθέγγομαι - phthéngomai - ftheng'-gom-ahee/5350\">G5350</a>; to <i>enunciate plainly</i>, that is, <i>declare:</i> - say, speak forth, utterance.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}